porech/pysamsung-dplug
https://github.com/porech/pysamsung-dplug

build_ssl_context() in custom_components/samsung_ac_drc/drc_client.py is taken
from this project's client.py. Both this module and porech's speak their
respective protocols over the same legacy Samsung TLS transport, and so need an
identical client configuration.

The bundled certificate custom_components/samsung_ac_drc/ac14k_m.pem is Samsung's
own shared client certificate. It is byte-for-byte identical to the copy in
pysamsung-dplug and in several other implementations of this protocol family; it
originates with Samsung rather than with any of those projects.

